title: David Jordan - Sun Goes Down [2008][MP3][Bradderz]
description:
If you are wondering where all the British pop superstars disappeared to, your answer may come in the shape of David Jordan. At only 21 this singer, songwriter and natural, effervescent live performer is throwing contemporary British pop in exciting new directions with searing rock guitars, throbbing party rhythms, blissful melodies and charismatically executed nods to his own childhood idols. 

Debut Single - Sun Goes Down. With his up and coming debut album "Set The Mood" Releasing Ealry 2008.
